##To make a class singleton, we first need to make its constructor PRIVATE and 
provide a public static method, which creates object of the singleton class.

#Order of Singleton classes and Test classes
1. SingletonEager - TestSingletonEager
2. SingletonLazy - TestSingletonLazy
3. SingletonTester --> to test if Reflection can penetrate Singleton
4. SingletonReflectionSafe - SingletonTester2
5. SingletonThreadTester --> to check if reflection safe singleton is thread safe or not. One of the outputs -
	instance1: 1530740446
	instance2: 927687912
	
